Maintainer: Jason Perlow <jperlow@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: nclawzero-rdp-init
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 openssl,
 passwd,
 adduser
Description: nclawzero first-boot RDP/TLS setup
 Generates a self-signed TLS cert for Weston's RDP backend and
 seeds the pi user's password from /etc/nclawzero/initial-password
 (default: 'nclawzero' — change after flash).
 .
 Creates /var/lib/nclawzero/rdp-init.done sentinel to ensure
 idempotent first-boot behavior. Safe to include in both headless
 and desktop images.
